{% comment %}
  birthdays.liquid — "Anniversaries" / birthdays section.

  Required variables:
    birthdays            array of {name, date, kind} — the dashboard-v2.json "birthdays" key,
                        in display order. kind is "birthday" or "anniversary".
    today               reference date as an ISO string "YYYY-MM-DD" (dashboard-v2.json
                        meta.reference_date) — used to show "Today!" instead of a
                        formatted date.

  Optional variables:
    error               Error message for the birthdays source. When present, an error view
                        is rendered instead of the birthday list.

  Device-specific variables (parent template must pass these in):
    max_birthdays        max rows to render (DeviceProfile.max_birthdays).
    font_size_medium     px size for the section title ("Anniversaries").
    font_size_small      px size for each row.
    line_height          px row height (DeviceProfile.line_height).
    padding              px internal padding.
    title                (optional) section title text, defaults to "Anniversaries".

  Note: the original PNG renderer shows a "(in Nd)" countdown next to each date
  (e.g. "Mon 20 Jul (in 5d)"). Stock Liquid has no day-count arithmetic filter, so
  this partial renders the formatted date (plus "Today!" when it matches `today`)
  and omits the countdown — see templates/CONTRACT.md for the full rationale.

  Usage:
    {% render 'partials/birthdays', birthdays: birthdays, error: errors.birthdays, today: meta.reference_date,
       max_birthdays: profile.max_birthdays, font_size_medium: profile.font_size_medium,
       font_size_small: profile.font_size_small, line_height: profile.line_height,
       padding: profile.padding %}
{% endcomment %}
<div style="padding:{{ padding }}px; height:100%; box-sizing:border-box; display:flex; flex-direction:column;">
  <div style="font-weight:bold; font-size:{{ font_size_medium }}px; color:#000000; margin-bottom:{{ padding }}px;">
    {{ title | default: "Anniversaries" }}
  </div>
  <div style="flex:1 1 auto; overflow:hidden;">
    {% if error %}
    <div style="font-size:{{ font_size_small }}px; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">(!) Not loaded</div>
    <div style="font-size:{{ font_size_small }}px; color:#000000; margin-top:{{ padding | divided_by: 2 }}px;">{{ error }}</div>
    {% else %}
    {% for entry in birthdays limit: max_birthdays %}
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:{{ padding }}px; height:{{ line_height }}px; font-size:{{ font_size_small }}px; color:#000000;">
        <div style="flex:1 1 auto; min-width:0; white-space:nowrap; overflow:hidden; text-overflow:ellipsis;">
          {{ entry.name }}
        </div>
        <div style="flex:0 0 auto; white-space:nowrap;">
          {% if entry.date == today %}
            Today!
          {% else %}
            {{ entry.date | date: "%a %d %b" }}
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
    {% else %}
      <div style="font-size:{{ font_size_small }}px; color:#000000;">No upcoming dates</div>
    {% endfor %}
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</div>
